main event: A bright object was sighted through an overcast sky, performing slow maneuvers and changing direction before disappearing.
interesting points: The observation lasted for 11 minutes,The object changed course and speed during the sighting,The object faded out and disappeared in approximately 0.56 seconds,The sighting occurred on February 16, 1960, at 11:00 PM,The last observer/witness was D Al-Virud.
